'''Bekhruzdjon Karimov''' ({{lang-x2|uz|Behruzjon Karimov|Беҳрузжон Каримов}}; born 7 August 2007) is an Uzbekistani professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[right-back]] for [[Uzbekistan Super League]] club [[FC Surkhon|Surkhon]], and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].

==Club career==
Karimov began his career in the [[Uzbekistan Super League]] with [[FC Olympic Tashkent|Olympic Tashkent]], before moving to [[FC Surkhon|Surkhon]] in 2025 where he had his breakout season.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://stadion.uz/uz/news/detail/540596|title=Behruz Karimov: "Maqsadim — yetarlicha tajriba to‘plab, Yevropa klublari va milliy terma jamoamizning eng muhim o‘yinchilaridan biri bo‘lish"|website=stadion.uz}}</ref> In May 2026, he fractured his leg requiring surgery.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://championat.asia/news/behruz-karimov-ibrohimhalil-yoldoshev-va-lazizbek-mirzaevni-davolayotgan-shifokor-bilan-suhbat|title=Behruz Karimov, Ibrohimhalil Yo'ldoshev va Lazizbek Mirzaevni davolayotgan shifokor bilan suhbat|website=championat.asia}}</ref>

==International career==
Karimov was part of the [[Uzbekistan national under-17 football team|Uzbekistan U17]]s for the [[2023 AFC U-17 Asian Cup]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Oʻzbekiston U-17 terma jamoasining Osiyo Kubogida ishtirok etadigan tarkibi maʼlum. |url=https://www.facebook.com/UzbekistanFA/photos/a.1256360527816960/6069835586469406/ |access-date=17 June 2023 |website=Facebook |publisher=Uzbekistan Football Association |date=4 June 2023 |language=Uzbek}}</ref> He also made the [[Uzbekistan national under-23 football team|Uzbekistan U23]]s for the [[2024 AFC U-23 Asian Cup]] and [[2026 AFC U-23 Asian Cup]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uzdaily.uz/en/khaydarov-announces-uzbekistan-u23-squad-for-afc-u23-asian-cup/|title=Khaydarov announces Uzbekistan U23 squad for AFC U23 Asian Cup|date=1 January 2026|publisher=UzDaily}}</ref> In March 2026, he received his first call-ups to the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]] for a set of [[2026 FIFA Series (men's matches)|2026 FIFA Series matches]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://uz.kursiv.media/uz/2026-03-24/behruz-karimov-hojiakbar-alijonov-bilan-raqobat-fifa-series-turniri-va-terma-jamoaga-chaqiruv-olgani-haqida/|title=Behruz Karimov: Hojiakbar Alijonov bilan raqobatga tayyorman|first=Sardor|last=Saidov|date=24 March 2026|website=Kursiv Media Uzbekistan - Kursiv Media Uzbekistan – O'zbekiston iqtisodiyoti va siyosati, biznes va moliya yangiliklari}}</ref> He made the cut for the preliminary national team for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/uzbekistanfa/reel/DYuz4KLthdD/ |title=Milliy Jamoa bosh murabbiyi Fabio Kannavaro Jahon chempionatida ishtirok etuvchi 30 nafardan iborat futbolchilarning roʻyxatini e’lon qildi. |trans-title=National Team head coach Fabio Cannavaro has announced a list of 30 players who will participate in the World Cup. |publisher=[[Uzbekistan Football Association]] |via=[[Instagram]] |date=May 24, 2026 |access-date=May 24, 2026 |language=uz}}</ref>

